{"tid":551586,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何志平同志再次保釋失敗[369]","createTime":"2018-02-05T23:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T09:41:56.000Z","uid":51271,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"1dae80dd5fe686565a888dba664997018759e015","tid":551586,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T23:18:35.000Z","msg":"涉嫌賄賂非洲官員，在美國被捕的本港民政事務局前局長何志平，在紐約聯邦法院再提訊，保釋申請被駁回。<br />\n<br />\n聆訊歷時超過一小時，何志平的代表律師說，何志平情願受審，都不想「蒙羞」潛逃離開美國。不過法官形容證據「極度強烈」，無保釋條件保證到何志平日後會如期出庭受審。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部日前向法院呈交文件，反對何志平保釋，又指他去年11月被捕後，執法人員蒐集到更加有力的證據。文件又指何志平約有800萬美元資產，即是6千多萬港元，形容何志平是富有及經驗豐富的商人，與中國有深厚關係，潛逃動機非常大。"},{"pid":"699424f6d6a937868b158bf99872776ec96c0ed0","tid":551586,"uid":54264,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T23:24:08.000Z","msg":"支那出動戰狼營救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cbdb5c7ffe5e05a8416402be94794997b01654","tid":551586,"uid":8048,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T23:25:52.000Z","msg":"唱國歌囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cf9a3f7b06dddd791a39f5b51738e729e3070b","tid":551586,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T23:32:05.000Z","msg":"condom 何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d46975fb3588fbc48ae95284647ebd312785b8","tid":551586,"uid":32675,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T23:35:39.000Z","msg":"吳京呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3cd49f24781de43ff6f24cf81c0cf4261a618ae","tid":551586,"uid":997,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T23:47:20.000Z","msg":"會唔會其實佢唔想走<br />\n支共夾硬塞比律師佢再保釋佢"},{"pid":"d7b9c323c33492f9280b7209ec58b39efcdef1a6","tid":551586,"uid":39013,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T23:53:17.000Z","msg":"說好的雖遠必誅...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cla